Ukren-t di lpusṭa.
Tewweḍ-iyi-d tebrat.
Ṭṭfeɣ-d tabrat.
Teɣli-yas tḍebsit deg ufus.
Uɣeɣ-d ṭeẓẓina n yiḍebsiyen.
Tsers-d lqahwa i yinebgawen.
Ɛerḍeɣ-d aḥbib-iw s axxam.
Ɛerḍeɣ lqut ɣef lmelḥ.
Lqut-agi d amerɣan.
Ixuṣṣ lmelḥ lqut-a.
Tesseww-d tiɣrifin.
Lhant teɣrifin s lebṣel.
Tḥemmel ad tels taqendurt mm yijeǧǧigen.
Tuɣ-d taqendurt turqimt.
Tɛemmer-d taqendurt-is n tmeɣra s tɛeqqcin.
Tḥar melmi ara d-taweḍ tmeɣra-s.
Tettraǧu tameɣra-s s ccuq.
